Package de.iabg.mesh.io

Class Summary
ASCIIMeshConnectionReader This implementation of MeshConnectionReader parses an ASCII file containing mesh connection data, namely the node connections.
ASCIIMeshConnectionWriter This implementation of MeshConnectionWriter writes an ASCII file containing mesh connection data, namely the node connections.
NastranBulkDataReader This implementation of GeometryReader parses a Nastran file containing geometry data, namely nodes, edges, triangles, and quadrilaterals.
NastranSetReader This implementation of KeyReader parses a Nastran file containing node subset data.
RigidMeshConnectionWriter This implementation of MeshConnectionWriter writes an ASCII file containing rigid mesh connection data, namely the node connections.
